Das Lied der Trennung K. 519
(A song of parting)
==================================================================

This Lied was composed by Mozart in 1787, the year of Don Giovanni and
Eine Kleine Nachtmusick, but also the great year of Lieder.  It is
related to the next lieder (Als Luise die Briefe ihres Ungetreuen
Liebhabers verbrannte, KV 520) both through the lyrics and the music.

Maurizio Tomasi
October 2005



